With the growth of Internet of Things (IoT), artificial intelligence, and other technologies, the robotics market is witnessing a huge transformation, thereby largely impacting the automotive and electronic sectors in a good way. The next-generation robots are said to have human-like qualities such as intelligence, memory, ability to learn things, recognition of objects, flexibility, and others. Adoption of robotic technologies in industries imparts benefits such as reduced expenses, flexibility, enhanced productivity, and waste reduction.